[48;5;237m[38;5;231m## 1. Responsibilities[39m                                                          [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m`@relay-assistant/sessions` manages the continuity unit that spans surfaces. A [39m [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231msession is not a conversation turn; it is the persistent identity context [39m      [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mwithin which turns happen.[39m                                                      [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m**Owns:**[39m                                                                       [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- `Session` entity — identity, metadata, lifecycle state, associated surfaces[39m   [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- `SessionStore` — CRUD + query interface for sessions; storage backend is [39m     [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231minjected via adapter[39m                                                            [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- Session lifecycle — creation, activation, suspension, expiry, resumption[39m      [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- Surface attachment — binding/unbinding surfaces to sessions; enforcing [39m       [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mone-session-per-surface-slot rules[39m                                              [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- Affinity — routing hint that prefers continuing an existing session over [39m     [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mstarting a new one when a returning user is detected[39m                            [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- Session scoping — sessions belong to a user, a workspace, or a combination; [39m  [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mscope is recorded but not enforced by this package (enforcement is memory's [39m    [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mconcern)[39m                                                                        [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- Stale-session detection — sessions that have not seen activity within a [39m      [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mconfigurable TTL are marked `suspended`; explicit expiry marks them `expired`[39m   [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m**Does NOT own:**[39m                                                               [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- Memory content within a session (→ `@relay-assistant/memory`)[39m                 [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- Message routing decisions (→ `@relay-assistant/routing`)[39m                      [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- Surface protocol or formatting (→ `@relay-assistant/surfaces`)[39m                [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- Multi-assistant coordination (→ `@relay-assis[39m                                 [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m… +1261 lines …[39m                                                                 [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mexplicitly define the contract shape sessions must satisfy when registered into[39m [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m core[39m                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m5. specify the minimum tests to write now[39m                                       [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mEnd the document with V1_SESSIONS_IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN_READY.[39m                    [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m---[39m                                                                             [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mSTEP OWNER CONTRACT:[39m                                                            [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- You are the accountable owner for step "lead-sessions-plan".[39m                  [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- If you delegate, you must still verify completion yourself.[39m                   [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- Preferred final decision format:[39m                                              [49m
